Detailed Description

cvmx_zip_cmd_buf

ZIP_CMD_BUF = ZIP Command Buffer Parameter Register

Description: This is an alias to ZIP_QUE0_BUF. The purpose of this register is for software backward compatibility. This register set the buffer parameters for the instruction queue 0.
